{"name": "sustainable_bmc", "type": "code/html", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sustainable Business Model Canvas</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            grid-template-rows: repeat(3, auto);
            gap: 10px;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        .box {
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .value-proposition {
            background-color: #0057b7;
            color: white;
            grid-column: 2 / 4;
        }
        .key-partners { grid-column: 1 / 2; }
        .key-activities { grid-column: 2 / 3; }
        .key-resources { grid-column: 3 / 4; }
        .customer-relationships { grid-column: 4 / 5; }
        .customer-segments { grid-column: 4 / 5; grid-row: 2 / 3; }
        .channels { grid-column: 3 / 4; grid-row: 2 / 3; }
        .cost-structure { grid-column: 1 / 3; grid-row: 3 / 4; }
        .revenue-streams { grid-column: 3 / 5; grid-row: 3 / 4; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Sustainable Business Model Canvas</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="box key-partners">Key Partners</div>
        <div class="box key-activities">Key Activities</div>
        <div class="box key-resources">Key Resources</div>
        <div class="box customer-relationships">Customer Relationships</div>
        <div class="box value-proposition">Value Proposition</div>
        <div class="box channels">Channels</div>
        <div class="box customer-segments">Customer Segments</div>
        <div class="box cost-structure">Cost Structure</div>
        <div class="box revenue-streams">Revenue Streams</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>"}

{"name": "sustainable_bmc", "type": "code/html", "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Sustainable Business Model Canvas</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        .box {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 2px 2px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #007BFF;
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        h2 {
            font-size: 1.2em;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Sustainable Business Model Canvas</h1>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="box highlight">
            <h2>Value Proposition</h2>
            <p>What are we offering to customers? How does it help them become more sustainable?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>Customer Segments</h2>
            <p>Who are our key customers? What are their values, needs, and worldviews?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>Channels</h2>
            <p>How do we reach our customers? How do we make our offer accessible?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>Key Activities</h2>
            <p>What are the essential actions needed to deliver sustainable value?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>Key Resources</h2>
            <p>What resources are required, and are they renewable or recyclable?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>Key Partners</h2>
            <p>Who are our partners and suppliers? How do they support sustainability goals?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>Revenue Streams</h2>
            <p>How do we generate value in a regenerative way? What pricing models do we use?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>Cost Structure</h2>
            <p>What are the key costs and investments? How do we ensure cost efficiency?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>People</h2>
            <p>How does this business support social well-being and under-served communities?</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
            <h2>Planet</h2>
            <p>What are the environmental impacts? How does the model reduce carbon emissions?</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>"}
